Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Hanekawa said Senjougahara lives in a mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was deceived by some weird cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She paid her entire fortune as tribute
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she racked up a large debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, my parents divorced at the end of last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I went with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I live here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save you, but I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean your body with cold water and change into some clean clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet here again at midnight. Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't play dumb with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're volunteering to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that makes you feel better, I'll charge a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does 100,000 yen sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awfully different from what I got charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I remember charging Class Rep-chan 100,000 yen too{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me for five fricken' million!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You became a vampire, I didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame it on vampires!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you afford it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 yen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished showering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please move or I won't be able to get my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on your damn clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'm going to put them on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've put them on before you came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to take them in with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least use a towel to cover your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's what poor people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen a girl's naked body...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think white would be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...patterned underwear and bras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you had dirty thoughts after seeing me nude?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did, it's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you can turn around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is just some special service to thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now she's mad at me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling me what you think would be the polite thing to do, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something like "You have a great body"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you're going to be a virgin for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the rest of my life? What are you, a time traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not spit while you talk? Virginity is contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can male virginity be transmitted to a female?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This topic is based on the assumption that I'm a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I'm being biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not spit while you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,STDs from hookers are contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine I admit it, I'm a virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll keep it a secret from Hanekawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Hanekawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the person who you have a crush on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you two talk a lot together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, that's just because Hanekawa is very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The most useless person is the most pitiful, they always have unreasonable losses."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the type of pleasant misunderstanding she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most useless person is the most foolish. That's truly a pleasant misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say that, so I wrote it on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like you could really set that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanekawa-san received help from Oshino-san before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:07:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm saying he's trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not only me who can prove that, but Hanekawa can too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I trust a person so easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many times I would've been tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I can't think so optimistically no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just put it on. Why are you taking it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to dry my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say such rude things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The consequences will be severe if you hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mentioned "optimistic" just then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't being more optimistic better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're doing something bad or tricking yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not doing something bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I am tricking myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "having a pattern the same as the moon" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say that to Oshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Japan, the pattern on the moon looks like a rabbit making rice cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in foreign countries, it looks like a crab or the side of a beauty's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you know such worthless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is first time since I was born that I've been impressed with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing, I'm just good at astronomy and space science.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in acting cool in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't know anything else apart from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about "verbal abuse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then call the verbal abuse police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:09:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to show off the body that you're proud of, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body that I'm proud of? I'm not that conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not good at wearing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you surprisingly know quite a lot, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps there might even be a brain inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say it's a miracle that a creature like yourself has a brain under that skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must think that I'm extremely dumb, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look genuinely surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of me that Araragi-kun\Ndiscovered how poorly made his brain is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that hopeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Academic performance rating check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is 74.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is 46...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be zero if you round that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! The unit value is 6, so{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you rounded using the tens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to my academic performance rating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't feel a sense of victory if we aren't 100 apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rounded yours using the tens too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If everything goes well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to Hokkaido to eat crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs taste very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshino-san, are you a priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I picked for my major in university,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't work at a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there was a lot to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, your clothes give off a sense of honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just making sure. You didn't put on make-up, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be better not to, so I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your decision was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun, you took a shower too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I took one at her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still as stubborn as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the pointless talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really so simple to exterminate that crab thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think too reckless, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something nice happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu-chan and the Perverted Cat attacked you and Class Rep-chan with malicious intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this crab is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Different?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you? It's a God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're going to pray to it instead of exterminating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Modestly pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we pray to it, will it give back\NSenjougahara's... weight? Her mass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not stubborn enough to refuse the sincere requests of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Gods are just a sketchy bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sketchy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't really care about humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To those Gods, our age, gender, and weight are no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that crab beside me right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's by your side, it's everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, in order to make it descend here, there are procedures we must follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, bow down your head and look at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're before an altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like drinking alcohol can shorten your distance with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little, it's not enough to get you drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's start by relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your own spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spot where it's only natural for you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the position with your head down and close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4, 5, 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7, 8, 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, now answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara Hitagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the school you go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoetsu Private High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When's your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,July 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your favorite author?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumeno Kyuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me stories about how you screwed up as a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What classical music do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that interested in music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you feel when you graduated elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to get into middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it was just transferring from one public school to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy did you have your first crush on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the most painful memory in your life up until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking about the most painful memory in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... My mother being...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...deceived by an evil cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Some higher up from that cult came to our house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother brought him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was some ritual...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He tried to assault...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to rape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by "tried", you mean it was just an attempt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit him with a spiked shoe that was next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my mother didn't save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the higher up was injured, my mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother was punished, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't resist back then, at least my\Nfamily wouldn't have become like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't have become so broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.49,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: 思い (feelings) and 重い (weight) are both pronounced omoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then those are your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how heavy it is, it's something you need to shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't transfer it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't{\fscx250}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't turn away, open your eyes and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I can't see it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I can see it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So isn't there something you need to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I need to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senjougahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My my, what an impatient God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just {\i1}so{\i0\fscx150} {\fscx100}friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something nice happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Oshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know, change of plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's just about your mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't make a request and if words don't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there can only be war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can say the problem is solved now that I've crushed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I could let it pass for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate crabs with a passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're hard to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Oshino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for what, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I was just surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are my feelings, my thoughts, and my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoulder them by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're something that I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me back my weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me back my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara's mother began participating in the cult when she was in fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Senjougahara had a serious disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to her daughter's illness, her mother\Nneeded a place for her heart to be at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara barely made it out of the operation alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of that, her mother fell deeper into the cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjougahara's relationship with her mother plunged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like she stopped talking to her\Nmother at the beginning of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she was about to graduate from middle school, that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a broken family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It became a catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Senjougahara met it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She met a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Araragi-kun, you know, heavy crabs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, heavy stone gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their name can also be read as "feelings and ties".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ties of obligation, that is. {lol shaftpuns}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, when Senjougahara met the crab, she cut the ties between herself and her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It erased her thoughts about her mother as worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped her from feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her weight was taken away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Willingly. She tricked herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't all that bad, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:22:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, even though you got your feelings back,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.37,0:22:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your mother isn't going to come back, and your broken family can't be repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even she knew that. Even so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this, Senjougahara Hitagi wanted them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really wanted them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those helpless feelings about her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those memories and troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it could just turn out like\NOshino said, and nothing will change...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And plus, this wasn't a waste of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I made a precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I offer you all my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for what I've done to you up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be shameless for me to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be very happy if we can\Ncontinue getting along well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, it's morning! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wake up or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just fell asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So you stayed up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who hasn't eaten breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:09.95,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is heavy... It seems like I've got a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I weigh 55 kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gods really are just a sketchy bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:23:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukihi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the preview quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:23:59.37,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bus driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:01.23,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the name of the bus driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:04.27,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too brief!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, Mayoi Snail, part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, it's your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.60,0:24:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a scam.
